{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/softwarebycl/awesome-contexture/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"55718822-7293-58eb-a824-44fc1b54535c","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-contexture-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-contexture-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome contexture awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Contexture <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture\">Contexture</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">15</span></span></a> abstracts queries/filters and results/aggregations from different backing data stores like ElasticSearch and MongoDB.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture\"><img src=\"https://github.com/softwarebycl/awesome-contexture/raw/master/contexture.png\" align=\"center\" width=\"1000\"></a></p>\n<p>Contexture is a tool for running the Contexture DSL, which is primarily about <strong>abstracting queries/filters</strong> and <strong>results/aggregrations</strong>. Each leaf node in a Contexture Tree can affect other leaf nodes (e.g., acting as a filter) and has results of it's own which are affected by the other nodes. Non leaf nodes describe how leaves relate to each other, e.g. as a boolean join of and/or. Contexture can use different backing data stores such as MongoDB and ElasticSearch.</p>\n<p>This page represents a curated list of Contexture websites, libraries, and resources. Our goal is to provide Contexture developers, both new and established, a place to discover and document awesome Contexture resources.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#websites\">Websites</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#libraries\">Libraries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#documentation\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#presentations\">Presentations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#videos\">Videos</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"websites\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#websites\" aria-label=\"websites permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Websites</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://contexture.site\">contexture-site</a> - Showcase of Contexture searches adapting to diverse datasets such as: car crashes, restaurant locations, COVID-19, SAT scores, school grants, bank failures.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-imdb\">contexture-imdb</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-imdb\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a> - An example usage of Contexture to present a search interface for an ElasticSearch index of movie records based on IMDB.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://app.govspend.com/\">GovSpend</a> - A Contexture web-based tool that makes it easy for government agencies to find a product's best price, identify and validate vendors, request quotes and connect with peers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"libraries\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#libraries\" aria-label=\"libraries permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Libraries</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture\">contexture</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">15</span></span></a> - The core library that exectues the DSL to retrieve data.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-client\">contexture-client</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-client\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a> - The client library that manages the DSL, allowing for hyper efficient updates running only what is exactly needed.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-react\">contexture-react</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-react\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a> - React components for building Contexture interfaces.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/grey-vest\">grey-vest</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/grey-vest\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a> - Component library built for contexture-react.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-mongo\">contexture-mongo</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-mongo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a> - MongoDB provider for Contexture.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-elasticsearch\">contexture-elasticsearch</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-elasticsearch\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a> - Elasticsearch provider for Contexture.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-export\">contexture-exports</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-export\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a> - A library that extends Contexture by allowing developers to export searches into files or any other target.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ltchris/contexture-api\">contexture-api</a> - A simple FeathersJS REST API for Contexture.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"documentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#documentation\" aria-label=\"documentation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Documentation</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.contexture.site/\">Contexture Docs</a> - Documentation of the entire Contexture ecosystem in one place.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://smartprocure.github.io/contexture-react\">Contexture React Storybook</a> - Contexture React components documentation and examples.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://smartprocure.github.io/grey-vest\">GreyVest Storybook</a> - GreyVest component library's documentation and examples.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture#example-usage\">Contexture</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture#example-usage\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">15</span></span></a> - Documentation on Contexture's core concepts, example usage, and implementation details.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-client#overview\">Contexture Client</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-client#overview\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a> - Documentation overview of the Contexture Client's features, api, and implementation details.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-elasticsearch#usage\">Contexture ElasticSearch</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-elasticsearch#usage\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a> - Usage and API documentation for the Contexture ElasticSearch provider library.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-mongo#overview\">Contexture MongoDB</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-mongo#overview\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a> - Usage and API documentation for the Contexture MongoDB provider library.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-export#index\">Contexture Exports</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smartprocure/contexture-export#index\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin